gg_fy_sewageworks_v1,1

 This is my latest map, it follows roughly the styling of my favorite UT3 map. Ambiance was what I was aiming for with this map. It is designed to be gloomy and dark to give that slightly creepy feel. It has HDR lighting for this effect and volumetric fog. Took me a while to plan out the basic structure and then a week or so to add the detail and textures to that. This ISN'T the finalized version, I will be working on the textures and adding more detail to the map, however I want to test the general layout first. Thanks for reading.
